&lt;li class=&quot;my-2&quot;&gt;Knowledge in transducer design and developing acoustic tests for laboratory and factory environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;my-2&quot;&gt;Familiarity with Android and Qualcomm audio debugging tools, including adb, QXDM, QACT, and AudioReach.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;my-2&quot;&gt;Understanding of transistor-level IC design and the silicon manufacturing process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;my-2&quot;&gt;Experience in audio speech quality testing and optimization using tools like B&amp;amp;K or ACQUA.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;my-2&quot;&gt;Experience with coexistence testing for audio within a full product (as victim or aggressor)&lt;/li&gt;
