&lt;li class=&quot;my-2&quot;&gt;Experience in tuning render system algorithms for consumer electronics, with a focus on critical listening and subjective evaluation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;my-2&quot;&gt;Solid understanding of electroacoustic principles, including speaker Thiele-Small parameters and frequency response interpretation.&lt;/li&gt;
