&lt;li class=&quot;my-2&quot;&gt;Monitor Neware dashboards for real-time tracking and status of tests and equipment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;my-2&quot;&gt;Assist the Lab Manager in providing samples or data to third-party test houses and external labs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;my-2&quot;&gt;Ensure the upkeep and organization of the lab, maintaining a safe and productive work environment.&lt;/li&gt;
