&lt;li class=&quot;my-2&quot;&gt;Demonstrated ability to follow standardized lab processes, including IQC and precise measurement protocols.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;my-2&quot;&gt;Strong attention to detail in recording test data and identifying anomalies during testing.&lt;/li&gt;
