&lt;ul class=&quot;list-disc list-inside my-4&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;my-2&quot;&gt;Exposure to or willingness to learn advanced analysis techniques such as CT scanning, cross-section preparation, and 3D measurements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;my-2&quot;&gt;Basic familiarity with Python, data logging tools, or SMbus communication.&lt;/

