&lt;li class=&quot;my-2&quot;&gt;Lead execution teams at CM/ODM (e.g., Huaqin Nanchang), ensuring accurate measurement techniques, thorough documentation, and robust adherence to established SOPs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;my-2&quot;&gt;Drive EE-level debugging and root cause analysis using Design of Experiments (DOE), collaborating closely with design engineering teams to identify, isolate, and resolve hardware issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;my-2&quot;&gt;Maintain real-time validation progress trackers, JIRA/issue documentation, and status updates for local and global stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;my-2&quot;&gt;Act as the primary communication bridge between external partners/CMs sites and US-based engineering, facilitating cross-timezone validation activities and technical reporting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
